* Carnage snarled, this clone was way to confident about itself!
She glared at Cyber Claw then stood still...*

" Carnage, Transform!"

* Once in her robot mode she bared her teeth at the clone, her vertebral 
spines twitched in annoyance!*

" Your forest?! I don't see your name on it anywhere! And I know the way to 
the Maximal base, I just decided to hunt for food and managed to run into 
you instead!"

* Carnage kept in mind that now that she was in robot mode the clone had 
more of a chance to strike at her and actually score a hit. Her bare stomach 
and back were the ideal places.*
